     <hotkey>h/<hotkey>?  Help<yellow>:<green> display this information
<white>Ctrl-<hotkey>C<green>    Enter Config menu
<white>Ctrl-<hotkey>O<green>    Enter Config menu

     <hotkey>w    Who is online
<white>Shft-<hotkey>W<green>    Short list of who is online
<white>Ctrl-<hotkey>W<green>    Toggle whether <hotkey>w will give a long or short format Who list
<white>Ctrl-<hotkey>F<green>    Online friends
<white>Ctrl-<hotkey>T<green>    People you talked to
