     <hotkey>:/<hotkey>;  Send Emote
     <hotkey>*    Send Feeling
<white>Ctrl-<hotkey>P<green>    Ping <white>;<green> see if user is busy
<white>Ctrl-<hotkey>X<green>    Message history
     <hotkey>v    Reply to sender of last received message
<white>Shft-<hotkey>V<green>    Reply to all receipents of the last received message
